divs: Sighting DetailsI was out on my deck with my camera looking for birds and the moon looked so clear I took a pic of it with the zoom lense.Came inside to the pc and looked at the pic.That is when I saw the small dot at the very top of the pic. I thought it was a planet so went out side and took two more pics.Nothing was there at tha time(abt 30 minutes later} Was showing the pic to my son and he saw another one lower down and to the left. They were not visable to me untill I saw the pic. The time is off in the info of the pic it says 3:30 AM but it was about 2:30 PM
